  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM1.10.3">
<l>empi rāṉaiyen taitantai tantaikkun</l>
<l>tampirā ṉaitaṇ ṭāmaraik kaṇṇaṉai</l>
<l>kompa rāvunuṇ ṇēriṭai mārvaṉai</l>
<l>yempirā ṉaitto ḻāymaṭa neñcamē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Our lord, our father, the father, the fathers’</l>
<l>lord, Kṛṣṇa with cool lotus eyes,</l>
<l>him on whose chest is [she with] a fine slim waist [like] a twig [or] a snake,</l>
<l>our lord worship, foolish heart.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
